    <!-- About -->
    <string name="about_title">About Holy Time</string>
    <string name="about_text">
        <![CDATA[
        <h2>HolyTime 1.0</h2>
        <p>Many people meditate about God and reserve time to Him each Sabbath (Exodus 20:8-11), but sometimes the job or other activities make to forget that Holy Time was reserved to enjoy His bless and company.</p>
        <p>Holy Time App helps you to not forget your communion with God and give you contents to read and meditate about His greatest love and forgiveness.</p>
        <p>Biblically the Sabbath begins and ends with sunset. So depends on your location, you will receive a notifications at the beginning the Sabbath to read and meditate.</p>
        ]]>
    </string>

